passionate, Most Merciful. Please bestow Your Blessings on Muhammad (s.a.w.a) and his Progeny (a.s) the Immaculate, the pure ones and may His peace be on them plentifully.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "SUBHAANA MAN SAWWA-MANEE A’NIT TA-A’A-ME WASH-SHARAA-BE WA MAN FARAQO-HU BE-MAA YO-WARRE-TONEE FEE ALEE-MIL A’ZAABE FEE-KHALLIS-NEE (YO-KHALLE-SONEE) MINAL E’QAABE BE-SEYAA-MIN WAA-JABA (AW-JABA) LE-YAS-SAWAABA BE-SEYAA-MIN LAHUL HAMDO LILLAAHE A’LAA AN HADAA-NEE WA A’A-FAANEE KAMAA YASTA-HIQQUL JAWAA-DUL KAREEMO YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA (WA SALLAL LAAHO) SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA A’LAA AHLE BAIY-TE-HIT TAIYYE-BEE-NAT TAAHE-REENA WA SALLIM TASLEE-MAN KASEE-RAN.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ مَنْ صَوَّمَنِيْ عَنِ الطَّعَامِ وَالشَّرَابِ وَمَنْ فَرَقُهٗ بِمَا يُوَرِّطُنِيْ فِيْ اَلِيْمِ الْعَذَابِ فِيْخَلِّصْنِيْ (يُخَلِّصُنِيْ) مِنَ الْعِقَابِ بِصِيَامٍ وَاجَبَ (اَوْجَبَ) لِيَ الثَّوَابَ بِصِيَامٍ لَهُ الْحَمْدُ لِلهِ عَلٰى اَنْ هَدَانِيْ وَعَافَانِيْ وَكَفَانِيْ كَمَا يَسْتَحِقُّ الْجَوَادُ الْكَرِيْمُ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ (وَصَلَّى اللهُ) صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّعَلٰى اَهْلِ بَيْتِهِ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ وَسَلِّمْ تَسْلِيْمًا كَثِيْرًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGree